{"title":"上哨所的小路","authors":["张可明"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":3,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上哨所的小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张可明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一条只有军人才走的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长的滑石板和拂了几代人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千刀树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也说不清到底有多少军人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步从这里走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有翻新了八次房顶的岗哨楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是一本记录军人生活的大全"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天早晨和夜里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会有战士小张小李……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用汗水写上小路的变迁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻开昨夜的记录"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能清楚地看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军也是从这里起步"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}